        <div class="ex-time">Saved 6 hrs/week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ex-card">
        <div class="ex-icon">🏥</div>
        <div class="ex-industry">Dental Clinic</div>
        <div class="ex-desc">Auto-send appointment reminders 24hrs before via SMS, log no-shows, trigger follow-up</div>
        <div class="ex-time">Saved 8 hrs/week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ex-card">
        <div class="ex-icon">🛒</div>
        <div class="ex-industry">E-Commerce Brand</div>
        <div class="ex-desc">Route support emails to Slack channels by topic, auto-tag priority, draft AI reply</div>
        <div class="ex-time">Saved 12 hrs/week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ex-card">
